As a retirement plan advisor you have the amazing, yet daunting, task of guiding investments in the approximately $4 Trillion US retirement market.
Helping your clients design well-constructed plans that may provide a positive outcome for their participants is critical. At Northern Trust we understand the challenges you face as you seek to educate your clients and their participants while providing sound investment solutions. Northern Trust manages more than $105 Billion in defined contribution assets for mid-to-large corporate plans. While the size of the plans you service may be smaller, the demands by plan sponsors and participants are not.
Northern Trust offers a diverse set of solutions that can help meet the needs of nearly any sized plan. These include a broad selection of index and active equity and income funds. At Northern Trust, we believe more can be done to drive financial success at retirement. Please take a look at our ongoing Defined Contribution research – The Path Forward – which reveals what plan participants think about plan sponsors’ efforts to help them achieve more desirable results at retirement.
Contact our financial intermediary consulting group at 877-867-1259 or reach out to one of our experienced investment relationship managers today.

















