Financial IntermediariesPlease contact the Financial Intermediary Consulting Group by email at intermediaryservices@ntrs.com or call us at 877-867-1259, open8 a.m. - 5 p.m. CT, Monday through Friday. 
24-Hour Account AccessYou can manage your Northern Funds accounts anytime, anyplace through our automated telephone system at 800-595-9111.
